Two comments:
1) CONFIG_CISS_SCSI_TAPE should be CONFIG_CCISS_SCSI_TAPE, IMO
2) is any locking needed in your scsi eh reset handlers?  recent kernels 
eliminate the lock that's been traditionally held around the handlers.
